## Context
The NCC piece (0012) cites the companion paper for full technical details.
The companion must be publicly available with a DOI before NCC submission.

## Actions
1. Upload PDF to SocArXiv (osf.io/preprints/socarxiv)
2. Set metadata: title, author, abstract, keywords, subject area
3. Obtain DOI
4. Record DOI in companion-paper-vars.yml for cross-referencing

## Test
DOI resolves to the uploaded preprint.

## Exit criteria
Preprint publicly accessible with a citable DOI.
